{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01GWToTK3yYf7i2UrfRVeZoj","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the app:\n- It's a busybox httpd serving on port 5678 with label `app: demo-app`\n- Serves from `/www` which has `index.html` with content \"hello\"\n\nBut there's a complication: the request path is `/app`, but the app only serves `/`. I need to use nginx's `rewrite` or `path` configuration to strip the `/app` prefix before forwarding to the app.\n\nThe ingress needs:\n1. A Service selecting `app: demo-app` on port 5678\n2. An Ingress with:\n   - nginx as the ingress class\n   - host `demo.example.com`\n   - path `/app` that rewrites to `/` using the nginx rewrite-target annotation so the app can serve the request properly\n\nI'll go with the straightforward approach: set the path to `/app` and use the nginx rewrite-target annotation to redirect it to `/`.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1045,"cache_read_input_tokens":30420,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1045},"output_tokens":10,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3ebb3304-8394-4120-8d9e-5ad467391e77","uuid":"20348fa3-8150-45ac-9135-27fcf07fa611","request_id":"req_011CcMSiXC3MA7dTNgNE59xv"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01GWToTK3yYf7i2UrfRVeZoj","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The app uses label `app: demo-app` and listens on port 5678. Since the test hits `/app` but the app only serves `/`, I need a rewrite rule. Let me apply the Service and Ingress."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1045,"cache_read_input_tokens":30420,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1045},"output_tokens":10,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3ebb3304-8394-4120-8d9e-5ad467391e77","uuid":"537871e0-cf03-403b-86d2-75ff21200aff","request_id":"req_011CcMSiXC3MA7dTNgNE59xv"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01GWToTK3yYf7i2UrfRVeZoj","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_018edro3aFKMesBnhhCtVfUi","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"kubectl apply -f - <<'EOF'\napiVersion: v1\nkind: Service\nmetadata:\n  name: demo-app\n  namespace: demo\nspec:\n  selector:\n    app: demo-app\n  ports:\n  - port: 80\n    targetPort: 5678\n---\napiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1\nkind: Ingress\nmetadata:\n  name: demo-app\n  namespace: demo\n  annotations:\n    nginx.ingress.kubernetes.io/rewrite-target: /\nspec:\n  ingressClassName: nginx\n  rules:\n  - host: demo.example.com\n    http:\n      paths:\n      - path: /app\n        pathType: Prefix\n        backend:\n          service:\n            name: demo-app\n            port:\n              number: 80\nEOF","description":"Create Service and Ingress for demo-app"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1045,"cache_read_input_tokens":30420,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1045},"output_tokens":10,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3ebb3304-8394-4120-8d9e-5ad467391e77","uuid":"aeddbe58-b537-46d0-a4d6-3cf91cf89118","request_id":"req_011CcMSiXC3MA7dTNgNE59xv"}
